      <title>【hexo】使用typora写文章时，解决Markdown图片存放问题</title>
      <link href="2021/01/22/%E3%80%90hexo%E3%80%91%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8typora%E5%86%99%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0%E6%97%B6%EF%BC%8C%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3Markdown%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87%E5%AD%98%E6%94%BE%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/"/>
      <url>2021/01/22/%E3%80%90hexo%E3%80%91%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8typora%E5%86%99%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0%E6%97%B6%EF%BC%8C%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3Markdown%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87%E5%AD%98%E6%94%BE%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<html><head></head><body><p>1、下载typora。</p><p>2、配置typora。如下图：</p><figure><img src="/2021/01/22/%E3%80%90hexo%E3%80%91%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8typora%E5%86%99%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0%E6%97%B6%EF%BC%8C%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3Markdown%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87%E5%AD%98%E6%94%BE%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/clipboard.png" alt="img"><figcaption aria-hidden="true">img</figcaption></figure><p>3、在hexo根配置文件（不是主题配置文件）中，设置post_asset_folder为 true。</p><p>4、安装插件 asset-image，它会自动修正md文件中图片的相对路径，以便能够在url中正确路由。</p><figure class="highlight plain hljs"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install https://github.com/CodeFalling/hexo-asset-image</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure></body></html>]]></content>
      
      
